{"tid":2095570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國教育部高校畢業生就業標準：打電競算就業，網民：維穩用心良苦","createTime":"2020-07-05T14:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T14:51:19.000Z","uid":112551,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db1ee8c1c4d70df70430d9f1bcd93e20de21591c","tid":2095570,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:25:09.000Z","msg":"目前多個地方教育部門與高校網站均發布了&ldquo;教育部辦公廳於嚴格核查2020屆高校畢業生就業數據的通知&rdquo;的文件。文件對高校畢業生的就業去向以及就業統計分類做出了明示，並在就業界定標準中指出電競工作者等人員屬於從事&ldquo;自由職業&rdquo;的人員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/07/20200705wzh_14/gamersky_02small_04_2020751920966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2020%2F07%2F20200705wzh_14%2Fgamersky_02small_04_2020751920966.jpg&h=2a6aa29d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在&ldquo;高校畢業生就業去向界定及標準&rdquo;中寫道：&ldquo;自由職業（編碼76）指以個體勞動為主的一類職業，如作家、自由撰稿人、翻譯工作者、中介服務工作者、某些藝術工作者、互聯網營銷工作者、公眾號博主、電子競技工作者等&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.gamersky.com/image2020/07/20200705wzh_14/gamersky_01small_02_20207519202FF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2020%2F07%2F20200705wzh_14%2Fgamersky_01small_02_20207519202FF.jpg&h=b82974b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，在自主創業一欄中，文件也將開設網店納入自主創業的就業範圍。<br />\n<br />\n網民反應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dre86aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdre86aa.png&h=771603c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XV0kcQq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXV0kcQq.png&h=cdc1ddf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dxOmJr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dxOmJr.png&h=98c0dc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjgjtoU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrjgjtoU.png&h=9881aa58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/778JU3A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F778JU3A.png&h=1746cb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好快到全民就業 厲害了我的國"},{"pid":"b4d001539a8ac4290ed42060cca0164c143c9339","tid":2095570,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"失業率0%<br />\n我国又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6dc51bd2637f6471ccf908fee5f1b896de08de","tid":2095570,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"你UPLOAD條片上抖音都算就業啦"},{"pid":"7f5228be3e311e1cdb0dfb5e39cb20d1b25e2a51","tid":2095570,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"電訊部不斷推反沉迷<br />\n教育部就話啲人係電競就業唔係打機<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b6b38a5867870134d495658ba5e2b7aa6ce07a","tid":2095570,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f5228be3e311e1cdb0dfb5e39cb20d1b25e2a51","tid":2095570,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"電訊部不斷推反沉迷<br />\n教育部就話啲人係電競就業唔係打機<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:38:17.000Z","msg":"沉迷還沉迷，電競還電競"},{"pid":"7fa2b7613a731dd0d5d443a36e895751be1da3c4","tid":2095570,"uid":6132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"：紙是包不住火的<br />\n：我國的紙可以<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"